{"tid":1597544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌 你班友唔好咁痴線啦好冇呀 我想買份報紙咋","createTime":"2019-09-27T03:56:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T11:16:32.000Z","uid":59151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ae146c887b5a2a6f11e1f4a8c46ddfd6802a3327","tid":1597544,"uid":59151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:56:01.000Z","msg":"八點出左門口 行到以家行左差唔多十幾間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入到去望下賣報紙個位 啲姐姐笑笑口同我講話賣曬<br />\n<br />\n有啲鋪我未入去睇就同我講賣曬 （心諗你又知我想<br />\n<br />\n買乜...）<br />\n<br />\n不過我都有望下係咪真係賣曬 我覺得姐姐其實係自私收藏唔肯罷出黎賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n救命 我真係好想要一份 （最好可以買兩份 一份拎黎<br />\n<br />\n過膠）到底邊到仲有貨 我願意比多一倍價錢收<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span>"},{"pid":"5acc299576fa39fd564c993198772ed8dbabf49b","tid":1597544,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:58:01.000Z","msg":"IQ 題： 927今晚愛丁堡集會夜唔夜？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1597498\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1597498</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"298072e7d48a7247889e16b5b7b240b02cc9242d","tid":1597544,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:02:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTwitter：@paullihkg<br />\n#followbackhk<br />\n#followbackhongkong"},{"pid":"e7e35ceedb33355f35a2a8c9a465ffa5c68f670d","tid":1597544,"uid":59151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:12:45.000Z","msg":"邊 到 仲 有 自 由 之 夏 呀 <span style=\"font-size: medium;\">呀</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呀</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呀</span>"},{"pid":"071a9a86b226206866682d272e5f2aaf33f0e03a","tid":1597